{
  "texts": [
    "The ML approaches have been successfully used to accelerate computational fluid dynamics (e.g.",
    "Bar-Sinai et al. 2019; Kochkov et al. 2021; Jeon, Lee & Kim 2022), develop improved turbulence closures (e.g.",
    "Ling, Kurzawski & Templeton 2016; Wang, Wu & Xiao 2017; Beck, Flad & Munz 2019; Duraisamy, Iaccarino & Xiao 2019), reconstruct turbulent flow fields from spatially limited data (e.g.",
    "Liu et al. 2020; Fukami, Nakamura & Fukagata 2020b; Kim et al. 2021), predict the spatio-temporal behaviour of turbulent flows (e.g.",
    "Wang et al. 2020; Fukami, Fukagata & Taira 2021; Zhang & Zhao 2021) and advance surrogate modelling of turbulent boundary layer flows (e.g."
  ]
}